        Parameters:
        language - Language/parameter file to use for the TreeTagger
        treeTaggerHome - Path to the TreeTagger folder
        annotateTokens - Whether to annotate tokens
        annotateSentences - Whether to annotate sentences
        annotatePartOfSpeech - Whether to annotate POS tags
        improveGermanSentences - Whether to do improvements for german sentences
